<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <!--浏览器默认在高速模式 <meta name="renderer" content="webkit"> -->
        
        <title>电力大数据可视化分析系统</title>
        <!-- Style -->
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/dva-mvn/theme/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/dva-mvn/theme/css/index.css"/>
    	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/dva-mvn/theme/css/login.css">
    	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/dva-mvn/theme/css/signup.css">
    </head>
    <body>
    	<nav class="navbar navbar-default navbar-inverse navbar-fixed-top" id="top_nav">
			<div class="container">
				<div class="navbar-header">
					<button type="button" class="navbar-toggle collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#navbar" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="navbar">
				        <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
				        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
				        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
				        <span class="icon-bar"></span>
				    </button>
				    <a class="navbar-brand logo" href="index.html"></a>
				</div>
				<div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="bs-example-navbar-collapse-1">
				    <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
					<!--<li class="active"><a data-nname="index" href="#">首页 <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a></li>-->
				        <!--onClick="gotoLogIn()"  onClick="gotoSignUp()"-->
				        <button class="btn navbar-btn btn-transparent nav-btn-other" id="login" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#loginModal">登录</button>
				        <button class="btn navbar-btn btn-transparent nav-btn-other" id="signin" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#signupModal">注册</button>
				    </ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</nav>
		<header class="head container-fluid">
			<h3>电力大数据可视化</h3>
			<h6>一款全新的数据可视化分析工具，帮助用户从数据处理开始，多方位、多角度展示、分析数据，发现数据背后的商机。</h6>
			<div>
				<button class="btn btn-transparent btn-large" id="login" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#loginModal">现在开始使用</button>
			</div>
		</header>
    	<section class="main_feature container">
    		<div class="col-lg-3 col-xs-3 col-sm-6 main_feature-obj">
    			<!--style="background: url(../static/index/11卓越的数据处理分析能力.png);"-->
    			<div class="main_feature-img" id="f-img1" style="background-image: url(/dva-mvn/static/index/11.png);"></div>
    			<p>卓越的数据处理分析能力</p>
    		</div>
    		<div class="col-lg-3 col-xs-3 col-sm-6 main_feature-obj">
    			<div class="main_feature-img" id="f-img2" style="background-image: url(/dva-mvn/static/index/12.png);"></div>
    			<p>近50种可视化分析布局展示</p>
    		</div>
    		<div class="col-lg-3 col-xs-3 col-sm-6 main_feature-obj">
    			<div class="main_feature-img" id="f-img3" style="background-image: url(/dva-mvn/static/index/13.png);"></div>
    			<p>方便快捷的交互模式</p>
    		</div>
    		<div class="col-lg-3 col-xs-3 col-sm-6 main_feature-obj">
    			<div class="main_feature-img" id="f-img4" style="background-image: url(/dva-mvn/static/index/14.png);"></div>
    			<p>轻量级的网页平台</p>
    		</div>
    	</section>
    	<div class="container-fluid banner" style="background-image: url(/dva-mvn/static/index/banner1.png);"></div>
    	<section class="product_feature container">
    		<div class="product_feature_1 row">
    			<div class="col-lg-4 col-xs-5 col-sm-6 product_feature-img product_feature_1-img" style="background-image: url(/dva-mvn/static/index/21.png);"></div>
    			<div class="col-lg-1 col-xs-1 col-sm-1"></div>
    			<div class="col-lg-7 col-xs-6 col-sm-5 product_feature-text">
	    			<h6>灵活的数据处理功能</h6>
	    			<p>支持多种数据类型文件导入功能，用户可以自定义可视化区间</p>
	    			<p>包含重命名、编辑字段等细致化的数据分析功能</p>
	    			<p>拥有多种数据表连接方式、数据排序、求和等丰富的数据处理能力</p>
    			</div>
    		</div>
    		<div class="product_feature_2 row">
    			<div class="col-lg-7 col-xs-6 col-sm-5 product_feature-text">
	    			<h6>丰富的数据可视化展示</h6>
	    			<p>近50种可视化布局展示方式，用户可自由选择</p>
	    			<p>数据与布局的自动感知匹配，帮助用户筛选合适的布局方式</p>
	    			<p>同一画布，支持多种类型布局展示功能</p>
	    			<p>简单拖拽，弹指间实现用户专属的数据可视化</p>
    			</div>
    			<div class="col-lg-1 col-xs-1 col-sm-1"></div>
    			<div class="col-lg-4 col-xs-5 col-sm-6 product_feature-img product_feature_2-img" style="background-image: url(/dva-mvn/static/index/22.png);"></div>
    		</div>
    	</section>
    	<div class="container-fluid banner" style="background-image: url(/dva-mvn/static/index/banner2.png);"></div>
    	<div class="container-fluid banner" style="background-image: url(/dva-mvn/static/index/use_flow.png);"></div>
    	<footer>
    		<button class="btn btn-transparent btn-large btn-black" id="login" data-toggle="modal" data-target="#loginModal">现在开始使用</button>
    		<div class="footer-info">
    			<p>联系我们：aishasha@bupt.edu.cn&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp&nbsp电话：87654321</p>
    			<p>地址：北京邮电大学教三</p>
    		</div>
    	</footer>
    	<!--模态框-->
    	<div class="modal fade" id="loginModal">
		  <div class="modal-dialog">
		    <div class="modal-content" style="margin:0 auto;width:450px;">
		      <div class="modal-body">
		      	<form role="form">
                    <div class="form-top">
                        <h4>登录</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-bottom" style="margin-top: 20px; width:400px;">
                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="userId_L">用户名</label>
                            <input type="text" class="form-control" id="userId_L" placeholder="用户名">
                        </div>

                        <div class="form-group">
                            <label for="password_L">密码</label>
                            <input type="password" class="form-control" id="password_L" placeholder="密码">
                        </div>

                        <div class="group-control input-group" style="margin-top: 30px;">
                            <div name="kaptcha">
                                <input type="text" name="kaptcha" id="kaptcha" value="" placeholder="验证码"
                                       class="validate-password required form-control" required
                                       aria-required="true"/>
                            </div>
                            <div name="kaptcha-img">
                                <img src="/dva-mvn/kaptcha/getKaptcha.do" onclick="changeKaptcha(this)">
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="checkbox">
                            <label> <input type="checkbox" id="remember">记住我
                            </label>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>
		      </div>
		      <div class="modal-footer">
		        <button type="button" class="btn btn-default" data-dismiss="modal">取消</button>
		        <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary" onclick="login()">登录</button>
		      </div>
		    </div><!-- /.modal-content -->
		  </div><!-- /.modal-dialog -->
		</div><!-- /.modal -->
		
		<div class="modal fade" id="signupModal">
		  <div class="modal-dialog">
		    <div class="modal-content">
		      <div class="modal-body">
		      	<form role="form" method="post" class="registration-form">
                    <fieldset>
                        <div class="form-top">
                            <div class="form-top-left">
                                <h4>步骤 1 / 3</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-top-right">
                                <i class="fa fa-user"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-bottom">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="sr-only" for="userId">用户名</label> <input
                                    type="text" name="userId" placeholder="用户名"
                                    class="form-username form-control" id="userId">
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="sr-only" for="password">密码</label> <input
                                    type="password" name="password" placeholder="密码"
                                    class="form-password form-control" id="password">
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="sr-only" for="repeatPassword">重复密码
                                </label> <input type="password" name="repeatPassword"
                                                            placeholder="重复密码"
                                                            class="form-repeat-password form-control"
                                                            id="repeatPassword">
                            </div>
                            <div class="modal-footer" style="padding-bottom: 0;">
                            	<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-next">下一步</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </fieldset>
                    <fieldset>
                        <div class="form-top">
                            <div class="form-top-left">
                                <h4>步骤 2 / 3</h4>
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-top-right">
                                <i class="fa fa-key"></i>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-bottom">
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="sr-only" for="name">姓名</label> <input
                                    type="text" name="name" placeholder="Name..."
                                    class="form-name form-control" id="name">
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label class="sr-only" for="email">Email</label> <input
                                    type="text" name="email" placeholder="Email..."
                                    class="form-email form-control" id="email">
                            </div>
                            <div class="form-group">
                                <label>Sex</label>

                                <div>
                                    <input type="radio" id="square-radio-1" name="sex"
                                           value="male" checked>Male <input type="radio"
                                                                            id="square-radio-2" name="sex"
                                                                            value="female">Female
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="modal-footer" style="padding-bottom: 0;">
                            	<button type="button" class="btn btn-default btn-previous">上一步</button>
                            	<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-submit">立即注册</button>
                            </div>
                            
                        </div>
                    </fieldset>
                    <fieldset>
                        <div class="form-top">
                            <div class="form-top-left">
                                <h3>步骤 3 / 3</h3>

                                <p>Activate your account:</p>

                                <p>Congratulations!</p>

                                <p>We have already send an Email to your mail box, click
                                    the link in Email to activate your account!</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="form-bottom modal-footer" style="padding-bottom: 0;">
                        	<button type="button" class="btn btn-primary btn-jump">跳转到Email</button>
                        </div>
                    </fieldset>
                </form>
		      </div>
		    </div><!-- /.modal-content -->
		  </div><!-- /.modal-dialog -->
		</div><!-- /.modal -->
    	<!-- Java Script -->
        <script type="text/javascript" src="/dva-mvn/js/jquery/jquery-1.11.3.min.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="/dva-mvn/theme/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="/dva-mvn/js/custom/index.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="/dva-mvn/js/custom/login.js"></script>
		<script type="text/javascript" src="/dva-mvn/js/custom/signUp.js"></script>
    </body>
</html>
